370
00:25:37,546 --> 00:25:39,979
Did you hear a man’s voice?

371
00:25:41,453 --> 00:25:42,794
Irin.

372
00:25:43,817 --> 00:25:45,571
The light is on.

373
00:25:45,571 --> 00:25:47,481
That’s true.

374
00:25:55,813 --> 00:25:58,019
