400
00:27:50,771 --> 00:27:52,577
- Sure. - Me, too.

401
00:27:52,690 --> 00:27:53,848
Let’s go.

402
00:27:53,848 --> 00:27:55,102
Follow me.

403
00:27:55,102 --> 00:27:57,102
Okay, let’s go.

404
00:27:58,964 --> 00:28:02,509
