507
00:35:56,377 --> 00:35:58,019
What did you say?

508
00:36:35,016 --> 00:36:37,108
It’s all because of Irin.

509
00:36:37,108 --> 00:36:40,810
Without her, my life would be better.

510
00:36:41,088 --> 00:36:43,641
